    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタインデー前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day before Valentine's Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、おはようございます！\nレッスンを見に来てくれたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ good morning‚ {user}-san!\nDid you come to see my lessons?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、愛。そういえば、例のバレンタインイベント\nリズノワの出演が保留になってたけど……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Ai…Oh‚ the Valentine's Day event\nLizNoir appearance was put on hold. ……?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、すみません……それはまだ決まってなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ sorry …… that hasn't been decided yet ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。今いるのは愛だけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. Ai the only one there now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、なんだか落ち着かなくて……\n私だけ早く来ちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm kind of restless ……\nI'm the only one who came early.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "体を動かせば、気もまぎれるかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it would help to move my body and take my mind off things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（……なんだか様子がおかしいな）\n（バレンタインイベントのことで何かあったのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…… Something's not right here.）\n（What's up with the whole Valentine's Day event thing?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "愛、悩みごとがあるなら、相談してみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ if you have a problem‚ why don't you talk to me about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}